      "title": "PRs per Release (batch size)",
      "description": "How many PRs are bundled into each release. Larger batches mean more changes ship together, which increases risk but reduces release overhead. Smaller batches mean more frequent, lower-risk releases.\n\nThis reuses the per-release PR count from the DORA Overview dashboard.",
